<p><b>Discussions</b></p>

<p>Debian user Lina asked, <a href="https://lists.debian.org/debian-user/2016/03/msg00074.html"><q>which files
took the space?</q></a> regarding what seemed to be hidden files in the local file
system. A discussion followed which give a bit of history and procedure as to 
how the mount command mounts and sometimes hides files. </p>

<p>Debian user Jude DaShiell asked about <a
href="https://lists.debian.org/debian-user/2016/04/msg00017.html"><q>running Linux
without a display</q></a>, which talked about headless server setup, dummy 
display, and screen readers.</p>

<p>Debian user Richard Owlett asked about <a
href="https://lists.debian.org/debian-user/2016/04/msg01040.html"><q>Multiple live
iso's on a single bootable flash drive</q></a>; discussion follows about the
possibility of doing so and a few tricks to make it happen. </p>


